%N A167757 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 32 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^15 = I.
%C A167757 The initial terms coincide with those of A170751, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A167757 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
